Package edu.umn.biomedicus.framework

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentBuilder  
    EagerLoadable  
    LifecycleManaged
    Indicates a class that has some kind of resource that needs to be shut-down or closed or freed at the end of the lifecycle of the application.
    NamedLabels
    Named labels of a TagEx search expression found during search.
    NamedSpans
    Named spans of a TagEx search expression found during search.
    SearchResult
    An immutable result of a search expression.
    Searcher
    Search results from TagEx.
    TagExMatch
    The a class TagEx search match.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    A class that provides access to the functionality of Biomedicus. The instances of this class is the "application instance" of Biomedicus.
    ArtifactSourceRunner
    Runs ArtifactSource instances.
    ArtifactTaskRunner
    Runs ArtifactTask instances.
    ArtifactsProcessorRunner
    Runs ArtifactsProcessor instances.
    BiomedicusScopes
    Contains the Guice scopes and contexts that store their scoped objects.

    There is one default scope:
    Processor Scope: contains objects that are one instance per configured document processor. For example, any processor settings.
    The primary method for running code in scopes are BiomedicusScopes.createProcessorContext.
    Bootstrapper
    Class which loads all biomedicus configuration and creates a Guice injector. Should only be used once per application run.
    ComponentSettingImpl
    An implementation of the annotation ComponentSetting so that it can be instantiated and bound to an instance to be used as an injection key.
    DataLoader<T>
    Loads data into, and functions as a provider for, a singleton object.
    DocumentTaskRunner
    Runs DocumentTask instances.
    DocumentsProcessorRunner
    Runs DocumentsProcessor instances.
    LabelAliases
    Maps labels to short aliases for SearchExpr/TagEx.
    LifecycleManager
    Service responsible for calling all of the lifecycle managed objects and telling them to shut down. Lifecycle managed objects will be automatically registered by the biomedicus guice module.
    RunnerFactory
    Creates and initializes runners for the different processor types.
    RunnersKt  
    SearchExpr
    Class used to search the structure of labels on a document to find specific expressions. Instances of SearchExpr are thread-safe but the instances of Searcher created against specific documents are not.
    SearchExprFactory
    Factory class providing for instantiation of SearchExpr objects using only their expression.
    SettingsTransformer
    Takes dictionaries of settings (usually loaded from configuration files, and turns them into a Map of Guice keys so that they can be bound for injection.
    TagEx
    A compiled search expression.
    TagExFactory
    Factory for parsing TagEx expressions into class TagEx objects.
    TagExKt
